113
00:09:13.791 --> 00:09:15.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Necesitará un barco.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:09:16.291 --> 00:09:17.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mihonoseki.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:09:18.458 --> 00:09:20.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debe haber dejado un rastro.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:09:20.666 --> 00:09:22.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Y si te mata esta vez?</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:09:34.583 --> 00:09:36.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Había sangre por todos lados.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:36.625 --> 00:09:40.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y por eso juré solemnemente</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>nunca más comer berenjena.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:40.666 --> 00:09:42.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuéntame de este barco.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:42.833 --> 00:09:45.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nunca viajé en barco.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Espero no marearme.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:45.375 --> 00:09:47.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me mareo en la bañera si chapoteo mucho.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:51.791 --> 00:09:53.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sigiloso por naturaleza.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:53.291 --> 00:09:55.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No hace falta que vengas.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:55.125 --> 00:09:58.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Y perderme cuando mates a Heiji Shindo?</c.bg_transparent>
