125
00:09:58.833 --> 00:10:03.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Al hombre blanco que protege.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Está en una isla al oeste.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:10:03.541 --> 00:10:08.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por mar, puedo llegar antes del amanecer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y matarlo al alba.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:10:09.750 --> 00:10:10.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Venganza.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:10:31.875 --> 00:10:33.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Dónde están todos?</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:10:44.125 --> 00:10:45.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Hola?</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:10:55.083 --> 00:10:56.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Dónde está la gente?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:11:25.583 --> 00:11:28.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No vinimos a divertirnos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sino a conseguir un barco.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:11:30.208 --> 00:11:31.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Claro, te puedo llevar.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:11:31.916 --> 00:11:33.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Gracias.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Espera.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:11:34.458 --> 00:11:35.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ahora no.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:11:35.833 --> 00:11:36.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mañana.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:11:37.041 --> 00:11:38.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y no muy temprano.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:11:38.958 --> 00:11:40.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debo partir ahora.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:11:40.625 --> 00:11:44.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿En pleno Hadaka Matsuri?</c.bg_transparent>
