139
00:11:44.125 --> 00:11:45.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Todos cierran hoy!</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:11:45.625 --> 00:11:50.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debemos purificarnos y honrar</c.bg_transparent>
