141
00:11:50.125 --> 00:11:52.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No quieres tener un mal año, ¿no?</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:11:58.541 --> 00:12:00.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bien. Mañana entonces.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:12:00.375 --> 00:12:02.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Así se habla! ¡A divertirse!</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:12:02.833 --> 00:12:04.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quédense para el Shingi.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:12:04.375 --> 00:12:08.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un chapuzón en agua helada</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>purifica el alma. No se lo pierdan.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:12:08.750 --> 00:12:11.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando escuchen los tambores,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>vengan corriendo.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:12:13.125 --> 00:12:14.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nos vemos en la mañana.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:12:16.166 --> 00:12:17.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No demasiado temprano!</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:12:20.416 --> 00:12:21.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo siento. Soy sigiloso.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:12:22.333 --> 00:12:23.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haces mucho eso.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:12:25.916 --> 00:12:29.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debe haber algo que quieras hacer</c.bg_transparent>
