152
00:12:29.458 --> 00:12:31.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Podríamos probar sus fideos!</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:12:31.416 --> 00:12:34.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡El Shingi!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Dijo que no podíamos perdérnoslo.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:12:34.125 --> 00:12:34.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tu pie.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:12:43.625 --> 00:12:45.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No debes sacártelo nunca.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:12:45.375 --> 00:12:48.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>El día que te lo saques,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dejarás de servirme.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:12:48.291 --> 00:12:49.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Entiendes?</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:12:53.458 --> 00:12:55.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Usaré este tiempo para entrenar.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:12:56.125 --> 00:12:58.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tú necesitas entrenar? Te vi pelear.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:12:59.750 --> 00:13:01.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Claro, nunca es suficiente.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:13:01.583 --> 00:13:05.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es genial perderse la diversión.</c.bg_transparent>
