162
00:13:06.041 --> 00:13:08.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Acamparé en los acantilados del este.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:13:09.458 --> 00:13:12.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ringo, tú quédate aquí y diviértete.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:13:12.708 --> 00:13:15.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por el tiempo que quieras.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Incluso por siempre.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:13:15.958 --> 00:13:19.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es deshonroso</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>formar un hogar y vivir tu vida aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:13:19.916 --> 00:13:22.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un aprendiz nunca se apartaría</c.bg_transparent>
