167
00:13:22.916 --> 00:13:25.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solo me divertiré un poco. Y mañana…</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:13:59.666 --> 00:14:00.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El corte.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:14:02.583 --> 00:14:04.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí me dejaste un rastro.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:14:10.625 --> 00:14:12.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Déjenlo pasar.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:14:52.958 --> 00:14:54.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡A las armas! ¡Cierren el portal!</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:15:17.958 --> 00:15:21.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los mensajeros debían encender una fogata</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cuando mataran al samurái.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:15:22.458 --> 00:15:26.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Contratas gente para hacer cosas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en las que no quieres pensar.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:15:26.166 --> 00:15:28.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Justamente para no pensar.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:15:28.208 --> 00:15:31.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es la razón de ser del dinero.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:15:32.208 --> 00:15:34.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No se puede confiar en cualquiera.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:15:34.875 --> 00:15:37.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Conozco esa premisa.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:15:39.458 --> 00:15:43.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cada año,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>te prometo placeres inimaginables.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:15:44.208 --> 00:15:46.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cada año, cumplo mi promesa.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:15:47.291 --> 00:15:50.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mi imaginación se expande.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:15:50.708 --> 00:15:55.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solo puedo salir de esta maldita isla</c.bg_transparent>
