182
00:15:55.125 --> 00:15:57.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estuve planificando todo el mes.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:15:57.875 --> 00:16:01.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorpresas para ti</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en cada parada del camino hasta Edo.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:16:03.166 --> 00:16:06.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Y cuando lleguemos a Edo?</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:16:06.083 --> 00:16:09.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nuestra sorpresa para el sogún</c.bg_transparent>
