186
00:16:10.333 --> 00:16:13.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Después de eso, podrás ir a donde quieras.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:16:14.708 --> 00:16:16.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando quieras.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:16:24.583 --> 00:16:25.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Listo.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:16:29.083 --> 00:16:30.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Después de todos estos años,</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:16:30.875 --> 00:16:32.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>dominas el pincel.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:16:33.625 --> 00:16:36.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odio la pintura.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:16:36.958 --> 00:16:38.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y el tallado en madera.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:16:38.666 --> 00:16:40.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y la cerámica.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:16:40.208 --> 00:16:41.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y la caligrafía.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:16:41.500 --> 00:16:44.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y las demás artes inútiles</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:16:44.958 --> 00:16:47.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>que dominé para dejar pasar las horas.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:16:48.750 --> 00:16:51.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odio tener tiempo para pintar.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:16:51.166 --> 00:16:54.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si tengo tiempo para pintar,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>algo anda mal.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:16:55.791 --> 00:16:59.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>El sogún nos deja operar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mientras pueda negar que existo.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:16:59.500 --> 00:17:01.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pronto no podrá darse ese lujo.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:17:03.208 --> 00:17:05.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quería el cuadro para mi cuarto.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:18:24.541 --> 00:18:27.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una espada forjada por ti no tiene precio.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:18:29.208 --> 00:18:31.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sin embargo, lo tiene.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:18:32.125 --> 00:18:34.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Toma todo lo que tengo. Por favor.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:18:34.458 --> 00:18:37.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debo tener una espada forjada por ti.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:18:39.500 --> 00:18:40.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No soy un espadachín.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:18:40.833 --> 00:18:43.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Encuaderno libros,</c.bg_transparent>
