208
00:18:45.291 --> 00:18:46.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>mi padre.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:18:46.583 --> 00:18:48.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo mató un </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ronin </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>borracho.</c.bg_transparent>

