211
00:18:52.625 --> 00:18:54.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ese </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ronin </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>es un borracho,</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:18:54.625 --> 00:18:56.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero es más hábil que yo.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:18:57.333 --> 00:18:59.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
