00:32:05.000 --> 00:32:06.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué no me defendiste?</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:32:07.041 --> 00:32:10.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Porque es imposible disuadir a tu padre</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cuando está decidido.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:32:10.791 --> 00:32:12.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Igual que tú.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:32:12.583 --> 00:32:17.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por ejemplo, cuando te obstinas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en hacer algo claramente perjudicial,</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:32:17.375 --> 00:32:19.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>como huir.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:32:19.416 --> 00:32:21.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Crees que no te conozco, niña?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:32:22.041 --> 00:32:23.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solía cepillarte los dientes.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:27.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No terminaré encerrada en Edo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>casada con un extraño.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:32:27.166 --> 00:32:30.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puedo arreglar todo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Solo debo encontrar a Taigen.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:32:30.291 --> 00:32:33.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Sola? ¿En un camino a la intemperie?</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:32:33.291 --> 00:32:36.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los forajidos te cortarán la garganta</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>antes de encontrarlo,</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:32:37.041 --> 00:32:39.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>si es que tu padre</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no te encuentra primero.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:32:39.625 --> 00:32:43.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En cuyo caso,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>estarás mejor con los forajidos.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:32:43.333 --> 00:32:45.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué alternativa tengo?</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:32:45.208 --> 00:32:47.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Compartir cama</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con un heredero del sogún.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:32:47.791 --> 00:32:50.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cualquier mujer moriría por eso.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:32:50.208 --> 00:32:51.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Les cedo mi lugar.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:32:51.583 --> 00:32:55.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esos hombres tratan a las mujeres</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>como animales. Dicen que es un tirano.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:32:57.666 --> 00:32:59.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué hombre no lo es?</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:33:00.083 --> 00:33:00.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tú.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:33:05.583 --> 00:33:07.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pon mi baúl con el de ella.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:33:12.625 --> 00:33:15.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entra y cierra la puerta.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:33:15.125 --> 00:33:18.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si vamos a huir,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por lo menos no pasemos frío.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:33:48.916 --> 00:33:52.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todos los días, durante mil años,</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:33:52.291 --> 00:33:57.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>hemos rezado frente al árbol</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>del que están hechos los </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>shingis</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:33:57.166 --> 00:34:01.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sus fibras están colmadas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>del aliento de los espíritus </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>kami</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:34:01.250 --> 00:34:03.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿A quién le otorgarán su poder este año?</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:34:04.333 --> 00:34:05.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Poder?</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:34:05.416 --> 00:34:06.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Son sagrados.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:34:06.708 --> 00:34:08.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La sacerdotisa los tira al agua.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:34:08.708 --> 00:34:12.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quien los agarre,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>logrará cumplir su mayor deseo.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:34:13.333 --> 00:34:14.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Palos mágicos.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:34:15.541 --> 00:34:18.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ni lo pienses. Son míos.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:34:18.083 --> 00:34:21.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Este año cumpliré mi deseo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Un nuevo esposo.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:34:26.583 --> 00:34:27.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Fideos!</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:34:34.458 --> 00:34:38.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Cómo están los fideos? ¿Ricos?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Los segundos mejores de la ciudad.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:34:38.916 --> 00:34:41.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eran los mejores,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pero Rinji agarró el </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>shingi.</i></c.bg_transparent>

356
00:34:41.791 --> 00:34:45.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Empezó a hacer fideos mágicos.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Aun así, son los segundos mejores.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:35:01.208 --> 00:35:02.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esto es…</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:35:03.416 --> 00:35:07.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Increíble. La densidad de los fideos,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>el sabor equilibrado, las especias.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:35:09.041 --> 00:35:12.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Es </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>shiso</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>? ¿Dónde conseguiste</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en esta época del año?</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:35:13.000 --> 00:35:16.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gracias. Recibo pocos cumplidos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>desde que Rinji me superó.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:35:16.500 --> 00:35:19.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Los suyos son mejores que estos?</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:35:23.958 --> 00:35:25.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trascendentes.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:35:25.416 --> 00:35:29.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sublimes. Nunca imaginé</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que un sabor así fuera posible.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:35:31.333 --> 00:35:32.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creí que era el mejor.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:35:33.625 --> 00:35:36.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Comparados con estos,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mis fideos son como gusanos.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:35:36.708 --> 00:35:39.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gusanos viscosos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de un estanque repugnante.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:35:39.500 --> 00:35:42.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No soy ni bueno</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en lo que creía ser genial.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:35:42.833 --> 00:35:45.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizás por eso me dijo que me quedara.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:35:45.458 --> 00:35:48.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya que te gustan tanto,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¿quieres trabajar aquí?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:35:48.250 --> 00:35:49.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los tazones se acumulan.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:35:49.750 --> 00:35:50.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yo te enseñaré.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:35:51.291 --> 00:35:52.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Quedarme aquí?</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:35:52.625 --> 00:35:54.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tienes un lugar mejor?</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:36:25.250 --> 00:36:27.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mañana morirá.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:36:49.333 --> 00:36:52.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los tambores. Iré a ver la diversión.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:37:18.875 --> 00:37:21.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No los conozco,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no tenemos ningún conflicto.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:37:22.000 --> 00:37:23.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tienes enemigos.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:37:23.666 --> 00:37:25.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enemigos ricos.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:37:25.458 --> 00:37:26.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puedes sacártelos.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:37:27.166 --> 00:37:30.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sabemos lo que ocultan.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Sabemos quién eres.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:37:31.583 --> 00:37:34.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todo Kioto habla del samurái sin nombre</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:37:35.000 --> 00:37:37.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>que masacró a todo el Dojo Shindo.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:37:44.208 --> 00:37:46.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tengo un nombre.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:37:46.125 --> 00:37:49.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nadie llegará a conocerlo.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:38:17.916 --> 00:38:18.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sí!</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:38:22.125 --> 00:38:23.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué hacen todos?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:38:24.666 --> 00:38:26.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Renacemos. ¿Qué esperas?</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:38:50.291 --> 00:38:54.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En los dojos pelean para presumir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Los guerreros peleamos para matar.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:40:29.458 --> 00:40:31.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cada año</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:40:31.083 --> 00:40:34.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>venimos aquí ardiendo de ira y aflicción.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:40:38.458 --> 00:40:41.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Permite que estas aguas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sacien nuestras almas resecas</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:40:41.625 --> 00:40:43.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y nos traigan buena fortuna.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:40:44.583 --> 00:40:48.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero solo uno de ustedes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cumplirá su mayor deseo.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:40:49.041 --> 00:40:51.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pidan sus deseos ahora.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:40:55.916 --> 00:40:58.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deseo destacarme en algo.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:41:15.125 --> 00:41:16.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Esposo!</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:41:19.666 --> 00:41:20.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No!</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:42:35.833 --> 00:42:38.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizás seas digno de mi verdadera espada.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:42:43.625 --> 00:42:44.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esa espada</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:42:46.000 --> 00:42:46.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>es robada.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:42:51.250 --> 00:42:52.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sigues siendo delicado.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:44:10.708 --> 00:44:15.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No merezco morir a manos de un impuro.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:44:16.291 --> 00:44:18.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Adiós, Chiaki el Carnicero.</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:45:00.041 --> 00:45:02.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me debes mi honor.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:45:03.291 --> 00:45:04.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ven a buscarlo.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:46:16.291 --> 00:46:18.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Subtítulos: Ezequiel Schmoller</c.bg_transparent>

